{
  "id": "61e91b382199d5001d170202",
  "title": "(4.2.4.1) Get information without reading",
  "created": 1551848331,
  "updated": 1555300634,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7de",
      "text": "(4.2.4.1) Get information without reading",
      "created": 1551848331,
      "updated": 1553661209,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7df",
      "text": "Before deciding whether to read a book X, you can know the position of the book X in the [context] of history. For example, Philosopher [Immanuel Kant] wrote \"[Critique of Pure Reason].\"",
      "created": 1551848337,
      "updated": 1551848652,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e0",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e1",
      "text": "Before the book, a mathematician [Gottfried Wilhelm Leibniz] argued the correctness of reason on the assumption that God is right. Kant took a critical position against the opinion. ",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848632,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e2",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e3",
      "text": "The book is a turning point of the history of the philosophy. ",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e4",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e5",
      "text": "A hundred years later, the philosopher [Friedrich Wilhelm Nietzsche] said \"God is dead\" in his book \"[Amazing Knowledge].\" Kant triggered Nietzsche to say that.",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848655,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e6",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e7",
      "text": "Even if you do not read these two books, you can know this information. This activity is collecting information about \"[a book that you have never read].\"",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848663,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e8",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848362,
      "updated": 1551848362,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7e9",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848374,
      "updated": 1551848374,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7ea",
      "text": "Next, you can [collect information] from the other people who read the book. You can ask your friend who familiar with the field. In these days, you can [search] book reviews on the Internet. By those ways, you can grasp the [rough content].",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848809,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7eb",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7ec",
      "text": "Even if you are convinced that you should read the book, you can read it [roughly] before you read it firmly. After the rough reading, if you do not feel the need to read firmly, you can stop reading there. ",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1555300634,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7ed",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7ee",
      "text": "If you think that you must read more books firmly than you can read, the thought accumulates suffering and stress. It is a more [realistic] [goal]-setting to let go of firm reading.",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551849176,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7ef",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848386,
      "updated": 1551848386,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f0",
      "text": "----",
      "created": 1551848389,
      "updated": 1551848435,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f1",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848435,
      "updated": 1551848435,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f2",
      "text": "I refer to many books in my book. If you call \"reading\" only the firm reading, I have read most of the books only once. ",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848421,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f3",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848421,
      "updated": 1551848421,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f4",
      "text": "Let me write it more concretely.",
      "created": 1551848421,
      "updated": 1551848421,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f5",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f6",
      "text": "I read the book at least once roughly before the planning of my book. I read it to the extent that I can recall there are concepts which worth to introduce.",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f7",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f8",
      "text": "Next, I read the book so that I can grasp what page I want to refer before writing the manuscript. It is the second time.",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7f9",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7fa",
      "text": "I carefully read the part to refer. It is the third time.",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7fb",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7fc",
      "text": "Writing a manuscript as reading make descriptions in excessive detail. So I do not read the book when writing a manuscript.",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7fd",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7fe",
      "text": "Finally, I read the book to confirm that my explanation is correct. It is the fourth time.",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f7ff",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f800",
      "text": "In other words, if you call \"reading\" including the rough reading, I read those books at least four times.",
      "created": 1551848346,
      "updated": 1551848346,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e000066f801",
      "text": "[en.icon]",
      "created": 1555300634,
      "updated": 1555300634,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    }
  ]
}